{"word":"G170 - ἀκαιρέομαι - akairéomai - ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee - Lack opportunity","slug":"G170","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκαιρέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>akairéomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Lack opportunity"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - akaire&#x0304;omai</b> - <i>ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2540\">G2540</a> (meaning <i>unseasonable</i>); to <i>be inopportune</i> (for oneself), that is, to <i>fail of a proper occasion:</i> - lack opportunity."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G171\">G171</a>, <a href=\"#/G2120\">G2120</a>, <a href=\"#/G2121\">G2121</a>, <a href=\"#/G2122\">G2122</a>, <a href=\"#/G2540\">G2540</a>, <a href=\"#/G4340\">G4340</a>"}]}